Package: khmerime
Version: @VERSION@
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Architecture: @ARCH@
Depends: ibus, python3, python3-gi, gir1.2-ibus-1.0
Maintainer: KhmerIME contributors
Description: Khmer romanization input method for IBus
 KhmerIME is a Khmer romanization input method engine. This package installs
 the IBus adapter, Rust bridge, and IBus component metadata for Linux desktops.
